The timeline expands the story chronologically, starting from birth, moving through the wedding, and concluding with post-wedding life.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Journey: A Chronological Timeline</title>

